I didn’t get this guys name but let’s call him MC for now because that introduction he gave me was too perfect.🎙️👌🏿

like MC said: I’m biking down Howard St. towards Broadway & happened upon this trailer. a GEM of a spot!💎 

Street style BMX’ng, my eyes are fixed for this sort of thing. Rails. ramp at an incline with wood laid over it.. My mind went Launch !! I did it once, then a second time with a beginning and end to the line. 

Someone said I made this look easy. True.
although there’s so much pressure riding street-style. Theres a small window of time I have to execute because MC don’t got all day for my attempts. The what-ifs..what if pedestrians jump out, what if the ramp ain’t as sturdy as it looks. Things beyond my control.
Only thing I’d control is my attitude.
“can you do it? YEA ! - Ight Get It !”

Shoutout to MC! A BIG VIBE !!
hope yall enjoy it.

🎥 : @dopepride
